    "comment": "I still believe that Intersect needs to find value in its membership if it wants to be sustainable in the long term. Right now, I would like to see that they have a process that reflects this and the fact that intersect is only one MBO ad not the arbiter of Cardano governance as a whole. Sepcialised DAOs and Alternatvie MBOs, even Independents will likely have better solutions specific to their areas of concern. I made my points directly to Intersect members in the past and this proposed structure goes against what my viewpoints are."
